{"tid":598741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"細個冇過踢區隊/青年軍，大咗真係唔使諗做到球員","createTime":"2018-03-19T18:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T01:35:02.000Z","uid":143768,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"626a23e89b5f6a51d4b52e1da721fe505446e979","tid":598741,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"係街場踢到曉飛都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做中堅既，9成未試過全力清波解圍。 屌你老尾，右邊就隔離場，仲有個呀伯慢慢行緊，向左邊清大腳啲就出馬路，搞到有車禍監都有得坐。 又成世人都未試過要keep住防線一致之類 大把野唔熟<br />\n<br />\n俾你日日去草場練，都起碼要幾年先叫掌握返啲11人比賽基本野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港真係唔會好似耶穌咁，上屆世界盃係街唔知掃地定上油，而家就踢緊曼城既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都係繼續街場跟隊算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726306198ab6dea2e5d02e275ef0494fcfd26bbc","tid":598741,"uid":108768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:47:16.000Z","msg":"關係好重要，如果有踢青苗之類 <br />\n同班教練/隊友熟左<br />\n之後想踢咩隊都一路順風"},{"pid":"08676570fae4f892d81702edd5a8c49cbae6d75e","tid":598741,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726306198ab6dea2e5d02e275ef0494fcfd26bbc","tid":598741,"uid":108768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:47:16.000Z","msg":"關係好重要，如果有踢青苗之類 <br />\n同班教練/隊友熟左<br />\n之後想踢咩隊都一路順風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:49:53.000Z","msg":"真係好似讀書揀學校咁一條龍"},{"pid":"17bb2bafae26ac23dab5114151a87170484b0689","tid":598741,"uid":162539,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"喺香港，無啦啦點會諗住做球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9358c7fed3a7b9e2c0a9c3eb9a0bc5c84d0d79fc","tid":598741,"uid":54122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"簡單講學界,好多平時街場好好波嘅,一上草場就馬上大打折扣"},{"pid":"4cd2d614dcc2cfe0c33a0c8c6a72757cd04ba498","tid":598741,"uid":36547,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep